                    <span>Wow! I can't believe what a great book it was.  I thought it was really great because of all the things the author put into writing this incredible book.  I read this book four times so far and each time the book surprises me more and more.  I think everybody should read it and get to raed an excellent book!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">DA BOMB!!!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
